    Double3x3

    Double4x4
    Record that represents a 4x4 double matrix.
    DoubleMatrix
    Class that represents an NxM double matrix.
    Float3x3
    Record that represents a 3x3 float matrix.
    Float4x4
    Record that represents a 4x4 float matrix.
    FloatMatrix
    Class that represents an NxM float matrix.
    Int3x3
    Record that represents a 3x3 int matrix.
    Int4x4
    Record that represents a 4x4 float matrix.
    IntMatrix
    Class that represents an NxM int matrix.
    MatrixAsDouble<M extends MatrixDoubleOperations<M,V>,V extends VectorDoubleOperations<V>>
    Interface to be implemented by a matrix that can be represented as a double matrix without casting.
    MatrixAsFloat<M extends MatrixFloatOperations<M,V>,V extends VectorFloatOperations<V>>
    Interface to be implemented by a matrix that can be represented as a float matrix without casting.
    MatrixDoubleOperations<M extends MatrixDoubleOperations<M,V>,V extends VectorDoubleOperations<V>>
    Interface that defines all base operations for double matrices.
    MatrixFloatOperations<M extends MatrixFloatOperations<M,V>,V extends VectorFloatOperations<V>>
    Interface that defines all base operations for float matrices.
    MatrixIntOperations<M extends MatrixIntOperations<M,V>,V extends VectorIntOperations<V>>
    Interface that defines all base operations for integer matrices.
    MatrixMathException
    Thrown when an application attempts to perform an undefined operation with matrices.
    MatrixOperations<M extends MatrixOperations<M,V>,V extends VectorOperations<V>>
    Base interface implemented by all matrix types.
